# {{project_name}}

Worker + D1, deployed via Cloudflare Studio.

## Live URL

After deploy: `https://{{project_name}}.<your-cf-subdomain>.workers.dev`

## Local dev

```sh
pnpm install
pnpm run db:migrate:local   # creates local D1 with schema
pnpm run dev                # http://localhost:8787
```

## Push changes

```sh
pnpm run deploy             # pushes src/ to production
pnpm run db:migrate         # re-runs schema.sql on the remote DB (safe — IF NOT EXISTS)
```

## What's wired

- `src/index.js` — Hono routes
- `schema.sql` — database schema
- `wrangler.toml` — config (don't edit `database_id`; Studio fills it in)
- D1 binding name in code: `c.env.{{d1_binding}}`
